CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1782319683
OL,3,CFormer beauty queen crushed to death
OL,4,Cby own car on icy driveway, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FA former beauty queen from Kent was
OL,8,Fcrushed to death by her own car while
OL,9,Funloading her belongings on a sloped
OL,10,Ficy driveway at her accommodation
OL,11,Fwhich had no barriers in place, a
OL,12,Fcoroner found.
OL,14,FAspiring social worker Eleisha
OL,15,FSkinner, 21, from Faversham, was
OL,16,Fstudying at Buckinghamshire New
OL,17,FUniversity and had reverse parked her
OL,18,Fblack Audi A1 outside the property in
OL,19,FHigh Wycombe on January 4 having
OL,20,Freturned from the Christmas break.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1782319683
OL,3,CFormer beauty queen crushed to death
OL,4,Cby own car on icy driveway, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FAs she unloaded the car from the rear,
OL,8,Fthe vehicle "slipped" and Ms Skinner
OL,9,Fwas pinned to a wall outside the
OL,10,Faccommodation, the inquest heard.
OL,12,FAnother resident at the accommodation
OL,13,Fcalled emergency services after he
OL,14,Fheard a "bang", a woman "scream" and
OL,15,Fshouts of "get off, get off" before
OL,16,Ffinding Ms Skinner unconscious, the
OL,17,Finquest heard.
OL,26,@pD@MOUpD@UO]vD@IOUvD@NO]vD@YOUvD@`O]wD@
OL,26,AKOUwD@\O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1782319683
OL,3,CFormer beauty queen crushed to death
OL,4,Cby own car on icy driveway, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FPolice officers at the scene noted
OL,8,Fthat the "sloped" driveway was covered
OL,9,Fin ice after wintry weather, making it
OL,10,F"very slippery", senior coroner
OL,11,FCrispin Butler told Buckinghamshire
OL,12,FCoroner's Court.
OL,14,FBut the driveway had not been salted
OL,15,For gritted and Mr Butler said there
OL,16,Fwas no barrier or railings in place to
OL,17,Fstop "overrun".
OL,26,@pD@JOUpD@QO]rD@AOUrD@OO]yD@FOUyD@NO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1782319683
OL,3,CFormer beauty queen crushed to death
OL,4,Cby own car on icy driveway, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FThe coroner said he will write to the
OL,8,Fowners of the accommodation, Howarth
OL,9,FProperty, whom the inquest heard has
OL,10,Fsince installed railings, so that they
OL,11,Fcan set out what has been done to
OL,12,Fmitigate the safety of the driveway.
OL,14,FThe firm wrote in a letter to the
OL,15,Fcoroner that professional inspections
OL,16,Fof the property determined that the
OL,17,Fdriveway was assessed as safe, the
OL,18,Finquest heard.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1782319683
OL,3,CFormer beauty queen crushed to death
OL,4,Cby own car on icy driveway, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FBut Mr Butler issued a prevention of
OL,8,Ffuture deaths report to Howarth
OL,9,FProperty amid concerns that an
OL,10,F"incident could arise where another
OL,11,Findividual could die".
OL,13,FThe firm has 56 days to say what
OL,14,Faction had been taken.
OL,16,FMs Skinner's car was in neutral, had
OL,17,F"no defects" and the handbrake was
OL,18,F"fully up", the inquest heard.
OL,26,@rD@AOUsD@UO]yD@AOUyD@LO]zD@AOUzD@JO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1782319683
OL,3,CFormer beauty queen crushed to death
OL,4,Cby own car on icy driveway, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FShe was taken to the John Radcliffe
OL,8,FHospital in Oxford but died on January
OL,9,F8.
OL,11,FA medical examination found that she
OL,12,Fdied from anoxic brain injury due to
OL,13,Fasphyxia compression, meaning pressure
OL,14,Fon her body prevented her from
OL,15,Fbreathing properly.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1782319683
OL,3,CFormer beauty queen crushed to death
OL,4,Cby own car on icy driveway, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FMr Butler wrote in his record of
OL,8,Finquest: "On balance, the incident
OL,9,Fappears to have occurred as a result
OL,10,Fof Eleisha's vehicle slipping after
OL,11,Fhaving been parked with the handbrake
OL,12,Fon and dropping off the rear of the
OL,13,Fdriveway, at a time when the boot was
OL,14,Fopen and Eleisha was behind the car in
OL,15,Fthe process of unloading.
OL,17,F"It was a very cold night with frost
OL,18,Fon frozen snow, which made the
OL,19,Finclined drive very slippery.
OL,26,@pD@JOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1782319683
OL,3,CFormer beauty queen crushed to death
OL,4,Cby own car on icy driveway, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,F"There were no railings or other
OL,8,Fbarrier or obstacle to prevent a
OL,9,Fvehicle over-run from the drive, nor
OL,10,Fwas there evidence that the driveway
OL,11,Fhad been salted or gritted."
OL,13,FMs Skinner, who had been crowned "Miss
OL,14,FFaversham" in 2022 and later "Miss
OL,15,FCongeniality", was described by her
OL,16,Ffamily in a statement read by Mr
OL,17,FButler as "kind, selfless and
OL,18,Fpassionate young woman, who always put
OL,19,Fothers before herself".
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@\O]uD@bOUvD@JO]vD@^OUwD@MO]yD@
OL,26,AKOU{D@VO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1782319683
OL,3,CFormer beauty queen crushed to death
OL,4,Cby own car on icy driveway, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FThey spoke of Ms Skinner's "fun,
OL,8,Fbubbly personality" which meant "she
OL,9,Fwas always the life and soul wherever
OL,10,Fshe went" and said that she was the
OL,11,F"kind of person who made the world
OL,12,Fbrighter just by being in it".
OL,14,FTheir statement added: "We will carry
OL,15,Fher with us always, our beautiful
OL,16,FEleisha, forever loved, forever missed
OL,17,Fand never forgotten."
OL,26,@oD@\OUpD@SO]pD@aOUrD@IO]sD@AOUtD@]O]vD@
OL,26,AXOUyD@UO]
