OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1782319683
OL,3,CFormer beauty queen crushed to death
OL,4,Cby own car on icy driveway, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FFaversham Carnival Club said: "Eleisha
OL,8,Fwas a fantastic Ambassador for
OL,9,FFaversham and a truly lovely girl. We
OL,10,Fall have some lovely memories of our
OL,11,Ftime spent with her.
OL,13,F"Our thoughts are with her family and
OL,14,Ffriends at this devastating time.
OL,15,FEleisha will be missed by so many.
OL,17,FBuckinghamshire New University said Ms
OL,18,FSkinner would be awarded a posthumous
OL,19,FBSc with honours in social work, the
OL,20,Finquest heard.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/11
